doc.after: The Pussycat Dolls had re recorded Don t Cha in Simlish as Do Ba for inclusion in the computer game The Sims 2 Pets 55 They also appeared in character form in the video game Asphalt Urban GT 2 released in November 2006 56 In a merchandising agreement with Interscope in 2006 toy manufacturer Hasbro planned a line of dolls modeled after the group reportedly to be marketed to six to nine year olds 57 Two organizations Dads and Daughters and Campaign for a Commercial Free Childhood successfully lobbied Hasbro to scrap the plan 58 saying they felt the dolls would have been inappropriate for children due to the overtly sexual nature of the Pussycat Dolls songs videos and performances 59 Also in 2006 Interscope negotiated a deal with Est e Lauder for a Pussycat Dolls line of cosmetics under the Stila brand 60 In 2008 Robin Antin and the La Senza Corporation produced a line of Burlesque Pussycat Dolls styled lingerie called Shhh by Robin Antin 61 and on December 15 Antin released Robin Antin s Pussycat Dolls Workout which composed of dancers from the Pussycat Doll Lounge Review including Chrystina Sayers from Girlicious and features Nicole Scherzinger 62
